WEBVTT

00:07:59.994 --> 00:08:03.720
I went home and said to my mom,

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:05.665
"You did something."

00:08:05.665 --> 00:08:08.551
This is not the African thing to do,
pointing at your mother,

00:08:08.551 --> 00:08:10.762
but hey, I was ready for any consequences.

00:08:10.762 --> 00:08:12.892
"You did something to me."

00:08:12.892 --> 00:08:15.250
She's like, "What are you
talking about, Khadija?"

00:08:15.250 --> 00:08:16.936
She's used to me mouthing off.

00:08:16.936 --> 00:08:21.111
I'm like, "Those years ago,
You circumcised me.

00:08:21.111 --> 00:08:24.594
You cut away something
that belonged to me."

00:08:24.594 --> 00:08:26.414
She said, "Yes, I did.

00:08:26.414 --> 00:08:29.384
I did it for your own good.